    "filesProcessed": 31,
    "description": "Complete CZO mapping for Commonwell Mutual Insurance Group. Commonwell is a single-version carrier (V134 only) with relatively few carrier-specific overrides. It inherits most mappings from the Generic base through V134 -> V133 -> ... -> v043 chain.",
    "versionRoles": {
      "V134": "BAU (current active service)"
    },
    "notes": "Commonwell has minimal carrier-specific CompanyConstants (only 3 constants: FireHallProtected='P', FireHallUnprotected='U', CSIONone='NONE'). No carrier-specific Z-codes. All coverage, endorsement, discount, and surcharge codes come from the standard CSIO enum value factory interfaces. The carrier-specific overrides focus on: (1) home endorsements (RoofDamageExclusion, VandalismMaliciousActs), (2) home liabilities (PremisesLiabilityRestriction, FosterCare), (3) auto endorsements (End13C inbound), (4) policy type mappings for various dwelling forms, (5) occupancy type (under construction, rented to third party), (6) exterior wall material (Log), (7) company code ('No Previous Insurance' -> 'NONE'), (8) fire protection classification (Protected/Unprotected)."
  },
